Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.17,0:00:20.58,Shinsou main,JULIA,0000,0000,0000,,{You think an apology will suffice?}Myslíš si, že omluva bude stačit?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:24.60,Shinsou main,JULIA,0000,0000,0000,,{We lost a valuable fighter.}Ztratili jsme cennou bojovnici.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.60,0:00:27.52,Shinsou main,JULIA,0000,0000,0000,,{Tsubaki, surely you understand now.}Tsubaki, ty to určitě chápeš.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:30.09,Shinsou main,JULIA,0000,0000,0000,,{We can't work with these sinners.}Nemůžeme splupracovat s těmito hříšníky.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.58,0:00:34.05,Shinsou main,JULIA,0000,0000,0000,,{Your naivete brought about this outcome.}Tvoje naivita způsobila tento výsledek.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:36.27,Shinsou main,JULIA,0000,0000,0000,,{They are our enemies.}Jsou našimi nepřáteli.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.27,0:00:38.47,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{You're wrong. We're not your enemies.}Pleteš se. My nejsme nepřátelé.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:40.41,Shinsou main,JULIA,0000,0000,0000,,{Ridiculous.}Směšné.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.41,0:00:44.47,Shinsou main,JULIA,0000,0000,0000,,{You were just betrayed by \Na woman you believed your ally.}Právě tě zradila žena, o které sis myslel, že je spojenec.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.47,0:00:45.72,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Yuri is...}Yuri je...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.08,0:00:48.73,Shinsou main,JULIA,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't wish to be stabbed in the back.}Nechci být bodnuta do zad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.18,0:00:51.05,Shinsou main,JULIA,0000,0000,0000,,{Never contact us again.}Už nás nikdy nekontaktujte.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.82,0:00:54.87,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Tsubaki-chan.}Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.45,0:00:56.24,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Here.}Tady.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.22,0:01:03.25,Shinsou main,JULIA,0000,0000,0000,,{We don't need your pebbles.}Nepotřebujeme vaše šutry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.25,0:01:05.18,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{Pebbles? These are—}Šutr? To jsou—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.18,0:01:06.54,Shinsou main,SURUGA,0000,0000,0000,,{What is it, then?}A co to potom je?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:09.36,Shinsou main,SURUGA,0000,0000,0000,,{Kurokami Marie is gone.}Kurokami Marie je pryč.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.36,0:01:12.34,Shinsou main,SURUGA,0000,0000,0000,,{You think returning that to us\N will make us forgive you?}Myslíš si, že když nám to vrátite, tak vám odpustíme?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.52,0:01:18.18,Shinsou main,SURUGA,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't have time for this.}Na tohle nemám čas.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.26,0:01:21.26,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Tsubaki-chan...}Tsubaki...
