Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.03,0:03:07.61,Shinsou main,RESEARCHER A,0000,0000,0000,,{Fog density stable at over 98%.}Hustota mlhy je stabilní při více než 98%.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.61,0:03:11.64,Shinsou main,DRAYLE,0000,0000,0000,,{Hey. Show your face already.}Hej. Tak už se ukaž.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.64,0:03:14.64,Shinsou main,DRAYLE,0000,0000,0000,,{You must be bored to death\N "conserving your strength."}Musíš se strašně nudit tím " šetřením síly ".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.70,0:03:14.92,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{Begin the test.}Zahajte test.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:17.92,Shinsou main,RESEARCHER B,0000,0000,0000,,{Artificial keystone 6, final test.}Umělý klíč 6, závěrečný test.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:20.13,Shinsou main,RESEARCHER A,0000,0000,0000,,{Resonance volume at maximum strength.}Hlasitost rezonance na maximu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.81,0:03:44.10,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Excellent.}Skvělé.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:47.99,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{A shame things didn't go as planned.}Škoda, že to nešlo podle plánu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.41,0:03:51.43,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Befriending an agent of Chaos\N was the pinnacle of foolishness.}Spřátelení se s agentkou Chaosu bylo pošetilé.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.06,0:03:53.80,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{"We can change fate"?} " Můžeme změnit osud? "
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.80,0:03:55.61,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Is this the result of that?}Je tohle výsledek?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:58.88,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Our relationship with the\N Guardian State is ruined.}Náš vztah se strážci je v troskách.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:00.59,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{What will you do now?}Co budeme dělat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:02.76,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't know.}Nevím.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:07.04,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Kurokami died because she trusted you!}Kurokami zemřela, protože ti věřila.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.04,0:04:08.79,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{And you "don't know"?!}A ty "nevíš"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:13.81,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{How many people do you have to kill\N before you're satisfied, grim reaper?}Kolik lidí musí umřít než budeš spokojenej, smrťáku?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.18,0:04:16.83,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm sorry, but...}Omlouvám se, ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.83,0:04:18.44,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{But what?!}Ale co?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:28.09,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{I was never counting on the\N Guardian State to begin with.}Nikdy jsem nepočítala se strážci.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.09,0:04:31.71,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Destroying Tokyo is the only\N way to save the world.}Zničení Tokia je jediný způsob jak zachránit svět.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.05,0:04:33.63,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{Kotetsu. Give me Kurokami Marie's blood crystal.}Kotetsu. Podej mi krystal Kurokami Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:36.47,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Huh? Okay.}Co? Dobře.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:39.17,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Where are you going?}Kam jdeš?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:41.76,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{To continue Inuki's research.}Pokračovat v Inukiho výzkumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:44.80,Shinsou main,KOUME,0000,0000,0000,,{This is the only way to save the world.}To je jediný způsob jak záchránit svět.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:46.93,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Tsubasa, let's go.}Tsubaso, jdeme.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.79,0:04:50.05,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{I have my own way of doing things.}Mám vlastní způsob.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.82,0:04:51.60,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Wait—}Počkejte—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:53.13,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Wait, Kakihara-san!}Počkejte, pane Kakiharo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.13,0:04:56.77,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Do you not understand your noble calling?}Nechápete snad své poslání?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:05:01.04,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Unless we destroy Tokyo, the\NHeroic Lineage will be annihilated!}Pokud nezničíme Tokio, hrdinská linie bude vyhlazena!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.04,0:05:02.31,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Is that what you want?!}To chcete?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.29,0:05:05.28,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{This was Kurokami's parting gift.}Tohle byl Kurokamin dárek na rozloučenou.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:08.50,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Let's revert the changes.}Pojďme zvrátit změny.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:11.04,sign_7404_58_Jonai_Municipal_,,0000,0000,0000,,{Midtown Municipal Park | Details\NToyoshima Amusement Park | Details\NMejiro Kusahira Nursery School | Details\NShinagawa Yatsuyama Bridge | Details\NChuo Yodobashi Wholesale Market | Details}Městský park Midtown | Podrobnosti \NZábavní park Toyoshima | Podrobnosti \NMejiro Kusahira Mateřská škola | Podrobnosti \NShinagawa Yatsuyama Bridge | Podrobnosti \NVelkoobchodní trh Chuo Yodobashi | Podrobnosti\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.54,0:05:12.99,Shinsou main,TSUBASA,0000,0000,0000,,{This is the AVAL Science Foundation's...}Tohle je vědecké nadace AVAL...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.55,0:05:17.75,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{It's the land they've been forcibly acquiring.}Jsou to oblasti, které získávají násilím.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.75,0:05:22.42,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Kurokami must have discovered something \Nand was killed at one of these locations.}Kurokami musela něco objevit a byla zabita v jednom z těchto míst.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:25.01,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{I'll avenge her alone.}Pomstím ji sám.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.45,0:05:27.10,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{This is where we part ways}Tohle je část, kdy se naše cesty rozcházejí.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:28.84,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Do what you want.}Dělej si co chceš.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.06,0:05:32.27,Shinsou main,TSUBASA,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't say you'll do it alone.}Neříkej, že to uděláš sám.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:36.56,Shinsou main,TSUBASA,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm your partner.}Jsem tvoje partnerka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:42.87,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{We'll start by compiling\N a registry of the list.}Nejdřív projdeme ten seznam.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.87,0:05:43.52,Shinsou main,TSUBASA,0000,0000,0000,,{Yes, sir!}Ano, pane!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:05:58.67,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{What do you think you're\N doing, Kamina Chihiro?}Co jsi myslíš, že děláš, Kamino Chihiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:01.67,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Have you come to kill me?}Přišel jsi mě zabít?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:05.05,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{No. I just...}Ne. Já jen...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:07.55,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{I bet you dreamed of my death.}Vsadím se, že jsi snil o mé smrti.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.14,0:06:10.70,Shinsou main,TSUBASA,0000,0000,0000,,{Is that true?}Je to pravda?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.07,0:06:14.77,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{What an honor.}Jaká čest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:18.82,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{I can finally cover one of \Nthe deaths you cause.}Konečně můžu být součástí smrtí, které způsobuješ.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.82,0:06:20.62,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{This is no laughing matter!}To není k smíchu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.62,0:06:22.13,Shinsou main,TSUBASA,0000,0000,0000,,{Kakihara-san...}Kakiharo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.13,0:06:24.32,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Your prophetic dreams seem unavoidable.}Tvé prorocké sny se zdají být nevyhnutelné.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.93,0:06:27.87,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{I couldn't write an article unless\N you let me know beforehand.}Nemohl bych nic napsat, kdyby jsi mi nedal předem vědět.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.35,0:06:30.24,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't want you to die.}Nechci aby jste umřel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:33.63,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{You're going to make me cry.}Ještě mě rozbrečíš.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.63,0:06:35.25,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Tell me how you really feel.}Pověz mi jak se doopravdy cítíš.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:37.25,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{You're not doing it for me.}Neděláš to pro mě.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:40.75,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{You're doing it for yourself and Shiraki Yuri.}Děláš to pro sebe a Shiraki Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.32,0:06:44.46,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{You can't change fate unless you can \Nchange your prophetic dreams.}Nemůžeš změnit osud, dokud nezměníš své prorocké sny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:49.09,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{And you can't change your\N destiny to kill one another, either.}A nemůžeš změnit osud, aniž by jste se vzájemně zabili.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:53.01,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I won't deny that.}Nepopírám to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:54.91,Shinsou main,TSUBASA,0000,0000,0000,,{You're awful.}Jsi strašný.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.29,0:06:57.11,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{I'm delighted to hear that.}Jsem rád, že to slyším.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.11,0:06:59.77,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Now tell me about how you killed your father.}Teď mi řekni, jak jsi zabil tvého otce.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.55,0:07:02.78,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't care if you hate me.}Je mi jedno jestli mě nenávidíte.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.55,0:07:05.41,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't like you, either.}Ani já vás nemám rád.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.65,0:07:08.74,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{But I have to do something.}Ale musím něco udělat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:10.73,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Nothing will remain.}Jinak nic nezbyde.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.17,0:07:13.76,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{We will change our destiny.}Změníme náš osud.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:19.16,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{For Inuki-san and Kurokami-san, \Nwho trusted us to carry on their mission!}Pro Inuki a Kurokami, kteří nám důvěřovali při plnění jejich poslání!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:22.88,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Kakihara-san!}Pane Kakiharo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:27.77,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{If you don't want me to die, stay away from me.}Pokud chceš abych neumřel, drž se ode mě dál.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.33,0:07:30.34,Shinsou main,TSUBASA,0000,0000,0000,,{I'll protect Kakihara-san!}Ochráním Kakiharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.69,0:07:37.65,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Those weren't the eyes of the Kamina \NChihiro I've been pursuing.}To nebyly oči Kamina Chihiry, které jsem sledoval.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.22,0:07:41.60,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{He's trying to live.}Zkouší žít.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.18,0:07:48.28,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{The plan is coming along smoothly,\N but it's likely we've been discovered.}Plán probíhá hladce, ale je pravděpodobné, že jsme byli odhaleni.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:50.86,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Tighten your guard.}Posilte stráže.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:53.69,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Lay out a trap and kill them.}Nastražte past a zabte je.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.69,0:07:55.78,Shinsou main,JUN,0000,0000,0000,,{Let me kill Kamina Chihiro.}Nechte mě zabít Kamina Chihira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:59.54,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{No. What can you do with eyes clouded by hate?}Ne. Co zmůžeš s očima plnými nenávisti?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.70,0:08:05.27,Shinsou main,HARU,0000,0000,0000,,{Wait, Jun-san!}Počkej, June!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.62,0:08:09.44,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Fool.}Hlupák.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.44,0:08:13.95,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{But it's true that Kamina\N Chihiro is an eyesore.}Ale je pravda, že Kamina Chihiro je trnem v oku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:19.01,Shinsou main,DRAYLE,0000,0000,0000,,{He did tempt your daughter, after all.}Nakonec, zlákal vaší dceru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.82,0:08:22.64,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{Though we were able to stop it,}Přesto, že jsme byli schopni to zastavit,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:27.02,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{the church and the Guardian State nearly\N forming an alliance was a thorn in our sides.}skoro se vytvořilo spojenectví mezi kostelem a strážci, které by nám způsobilo potíže.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.47,0:08:30.56,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{And at the center of it all was Kamina Chihiro.}A ve středu toho všeho byl Kamina Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:34.15,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{It was only temporary, but\N he united the Heroic Lineage.}Sice to bylo jen dočasně, ale podařilo se spojit hrdinskou linii.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.02,0:08:37.88,Shinsou main,GRUMMAN,0000,0000,0000,,{He may have what it takes to\N become the Lord of Vermilion.}Možná má co je potřeba, aby se stal Vermilionským lordem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.03,0:08:47.24,Shinsou main,YURI,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro-kun...}Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.12,0:08:52.71,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Kakihara's next?}Dalším je Kakihara?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:56.21,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Yeah. Chihiro-san said he dreamed it.}Jo. Chihiro říkal, že se mu o tom zdálo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.21,0:08:58.72,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{And he's trying to stop it alone?}A pokouší se to zastavit sám?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.17,0:09:00.60,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{What should we do?}Co bychom měli udělat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:03.55,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Are you asking me as a member \Nof the Guardian State?}Ptáš se mě jako strážkyně?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.55,0:09:06.13,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Or as Manazuru Tsubaki?}Nebo jako Manazuru Tsubaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.13,0:09:06.85,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Huh?}Co?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.51,0:09:11.11,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't mind helping out a friend.}Nevadí mi pomáhat příteli.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.81,0:09:15.24,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{What did Kurokami find?}Co Kurokami našla?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:19.74,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{The message she left Manazuru\N Tsubaki was her last communication.}Zpráva, kterou zanechala Manazuru Tsubaki byla její poslední kontakt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.54,0:09:22.33,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Her call history...}Její historie volání...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.45,0:09:25.21,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Her history?}Její historie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:35.63,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Come to think of it, you never get mad.}Když tak nad tím přemýšlím, nikdy se nenaštveš.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.89,0:09:38.89,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Are you in there, Tsubasa?}Jsi tam, Tsubaso?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.27,0:09:43.60,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Is this...}Je to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:50.53,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{A coincidence?}Náhoda?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.71,0:09:57.01,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{No. Shoko had us break\N the barriers to destroy Tokyo.}Ne. Shoko chtěla abychom zničili bariéry k zničení Tokia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.87,0:10:01.14,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{The barriers, huh?}Bariéry, co?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.19,0:10:07.11,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{You never give up.}Nikdy se nevzdáš.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.57,0:10:11.02,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{What did you want to discuss?}Co jste chtěl probrat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.02,0:10:13.84,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't make me laugh.}Nenech se vysmát.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:16.47,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{You're the one following me.}Ty jsi ten kdo mě sleduje.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.05,0:10:18.93,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I just want to protect you.}Chci vás jen ochránit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.93,0:10:21.81,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Well, either way, I was supposed to die.}No, tak jako tak. Byl jsem připraven zemřít.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.81,0:10:24.59,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{I wouldn't regret dying at this point.}Nevadilo by mi umřít zrovna teď.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:30.19,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{I survived a family suicide, too.}Taky jsem přežil rodinnou sebevraždu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:33.94,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Forced into it by debt.}Donucenou dluhy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:39.99,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{In the end, I was abandoned.}Nakonec, jsem byl opuštěn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:42.30,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{I was a precocious brat.}Jako kluk jsem měl za ušima
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.60,0:10:45.45,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{I knew my parents didn't like me,}Věděl jsem, že mě rodiče neměli rádi,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.64,0:10:50.96,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{but I still don't know why they left me.}ale pořád nevím proč mě opustili.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:59.22,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Why did you refuse to die with him?}Proč jsi odmítl umřít s ním?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:02.71,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Your father wanted to take you with him.}Tvůj otec tě chtěl vzít sebou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.71,0:11:04.82,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Why did you reject his feelings?}Proč jste odmítl jeho pocity?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.20,0:11:12.79,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Were you so reluctant to die that\N you were willing to kill your father?}To ses tolik bál smrti, že jsi radši svého otce zabil?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.29,0:11:15.26,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{You killed him, didn't you?}Zabil jsi ho, že?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.26,0:11:17.69,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{You killed your own father so you could live!}Zabil jsi svého vlastního otce, aby jsi mohl žít!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:19.61,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't care about living!}Nestarám se o žití.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.88,0:11:20.96,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{What?}Co?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:24.63,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't remember what happened that day.}Nepamatuju si co se ten den stalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.63,0:11:27.28,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{But I've suffered ever since then!}Ale od té doby trpím!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.74,0:11:30.18,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{When I think that I may \Nhave killed my father,}Když pomyslím, že jsem možná zabil svého otce,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.86,0:11:35.63,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I really wish I would've died instead!}Přál bych si zemřít s ním!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.57,0:11:39.63,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{But there must be some reason I survived!}Ale musí být důvod, proč jsem přežil!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.61,0:11:46.97,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{So I can't die yet.}Takže, ještě umřít nemůžu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:50.30,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Those are the eyes.}To jsou ty oči.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.77,0:11:51.89,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Why?}Proč?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.18,0:11:58.53,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Your eyes were always dark,\N no matter how cheerful you acted.}Tvé oči byly vždy temné, bezohledu na to jak jsi se choval.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.87,0:12:00.65,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Regret and despair.}Lítost a zoufalství.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.19,0:12:04.86,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{I sensed that you sought forgiveness}Cítil jsem, že jsi hledal odpuštění
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.55,0:12:08.29,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{even though you killed your own father.}i když jsi zabil svého otce.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:10.43,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{I couldn't forgive you.}Nemhol jsem ti odpustit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:15.00,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{If you were going to despair,\N why didn't you die with your father?}Když jsi byl tak zoufalý, proč jsi nezemřel s tvým otcem?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:18.30,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{You wanna live? Then don't walk around\N looking like you've got no hope left!}Chceš žít? Tak tu nepochoduj bez naděje.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:22.80,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't care who forgives you. I never will!}Je mi jedno kdo ti odpustí. Já nikdy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.54,0:12:29.34,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Or so I thought.}Nebo to jsem si myslel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.62,0:12:33.78,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{But you have the eyes of a man trying to live.}Ale tvoje oči jsou muže, co chce žít.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.34,0:12:38.18,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Even after being betrayed by a woman,\N being abandoned by your friends,}I poté co jsi byl zrazen ženou, opuštěn svými přáteli,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.99,0:12:41.45,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{and losing everything.}a ztratil všechno.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.31,0:12:47.36,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Did you really kill your father?}Opravdu jsi zabil svého otce?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:51.17,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{What are we doing here?}Co tu děláme?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:55.83,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{There were GPS coordinates\N on Kurokami's call history.}Tohle byly GPS souřadnice v historii volání Kurokami.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:12:58.28,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Did you call anyone?}Zavolal jsi někomu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:12:59.95,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Kotetsu.}Kotetsuovi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.78,0:13:05.04,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Kakihara-san, why did you talk to me last night?}Pane Kakiharo, proč jste se mnou včera v noci mluvil?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.04,0:13:07.72,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Because I wanted to know the truth.}Protože jsem chtěl znát pravdu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:09.68,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{Kakihara, you're a journalist.}Kakiharo, jsi novinář.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.68,0:13:12.68,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{Can you see the truth\N through those warped eyes?}Dokážeš vidět přes ty tvé pokřivené oči pravdu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.13,0:13:17.15,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't know why I told you that.}Nevím, proč jsem ti to řekl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.70,0:13:21.49,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{I don't know why I'm here walking with you.}Nevím proč s tebou jdu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:27.24,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{But if I leave things there,\N then I'm no journalist at all.}Ale jak nechám věci běžet, potom nejsem novinářem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.85,0:13:31.52,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{You think there's a reason you survived, huh?}Myslíš, že to je důvodem proč jsi přežil?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.52,0:13:32.32,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Yes.}Ano.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.64,0:13:41.17,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{This device probably\N creates artificial barriers.}Toto zařízení pravděpodobně vytváří umělé bariéry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:42.58,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Barriers?}Bariéry?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.58,0:13:46.12,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Based on the data Kurokami left,}Na základě údajů, které po sobě Kurokami zanechala,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.61,0:13:49.42,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{seven similar devices likely \Nexist around the city.}sedm podobných zařízení existuje po celém městě.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:51.75,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{What does this mean?}Co tím myslíte?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.11,0:13:56.69,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{They're trying to build\N new barriers themselves.}Snaží se vytvořit nové bariéry po svém.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:14:01.19,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{There's no point in Shoko trying\N so hard to destroy the old ones.}Nemá smysl, aby se Shoko snažila zničit ty staré.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:03.69,Shinsou main,TSUBASA,0000,0000,0000,,{Is that what the machine is for?}Proto tu je ten stoj?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.14,0:14:06.93,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{This is for something else.}To je na něco jiného.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.50,0:14:09.36,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{For their next big plan.}Pro jejich další velký plán.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:11.80,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{The Second Great Collapse.}Druhé velké zhroucení.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.80,0:14:13.62,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Correct.}Přesně.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:19.39,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{But, poor Icarus, you've\N flown too close to the sun.}Ale, chudáku Icare, letěl jsi moc blízko ke slunci.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:21.17,Shinsou main,TSUBASA,0000,0000,0000,,{Look out!}Pozor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:25.55,Shinsou main,TSUBASA,0000,0000,0000,,{Kakihara-san, I will protect you!}Kakiharo, já tě ochráním.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:30.87,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Kark Kaburagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.87,0:14:32.44,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{You know him?}Znáte ho?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.44,0:14:35.46,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{You don't? He's a famous pianist.}Ty ne? Je to skvělý pianista.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.46,0:14:37.27,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Even I've got his CD's.}Dokonce i mám jeho CDčka.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:41.69,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{The world calls me a decadent musician.}Svět mě nazývá dekadentním hudebníkem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.69,0:14:47.28,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Now, listen and die to the beautiful\N requiem I offer up to you.}Nyní slyšte a umřete při pohřební písni, kterou vám nabízím.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.55,0:14:50.70,Shinsou main,AERO,0000,0000,0000,,{No, you don't!}Ne, to neuděláš!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.34,0:14:55.35,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Tsubasa!}Tsubaso!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.35,0:14:56.98,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{How'd she hit her from there?}Jak by jí odtamtud mohl trefit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:14:59.00,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{You're the one who killed Kurokami.}Ty jsi ten kdo zabil Kurokami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.47,0:15:04.70,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{The reaper doesn't remember\N all those he's granted death.}Smrťák si nepamatuje všechny jenž poskytnul smrt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:06.76,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Bastard...}Šmejde...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:12.47,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Death comes for all.}Smrt jsi přijde pro všechny.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:18.14,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Dad?}Tati?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.08,0:15:28.03,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{What's wrong?}Co se děje?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:30.95,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{No...}Ne...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:33.91,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't, Dad.}Přestaň, tati.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:40.16,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Pull yourself together, Kamina!}Vzpamatuj se, Kamino!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:45.42,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{What do you think of the title "Binding Spell?"}Co si myslíte o názvu "Vázací kouzlo?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:47.77,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Break his spell!}Zlom jeho kouzlo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.77,0:15:50.17,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{That should be easy with your power!}Mělo by to být snadné s tvou silou.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:53.66,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I can't manifest my blood armaments!}Nemůžu zhmotnit svou krevní výzbroj.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.66,0:15:54.64,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{What?}Cože?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:57.76,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{My melodies capture people's hearts.}Mé melodie chytají lidská srdce.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:16:00.43,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{You must be very guilty.}Musíš být velmi vinný.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:03.27,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Your heart refuses to break free.}Tvé srdce se odmítá osvobodit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.27,0:16:05.67,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Kakihara-san?}Pane Kakiharo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.67,0:16:07.73,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Why am I doing this?}Proč tohle dělám?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:11.24,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{The unwelcome disrupt my beautiful melodies.}Nevítané narušení mých krásných melodií.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.94,0:16:14.47,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Run! Quickly!}Utečte! Rychle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.46,0:16:17.83,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{I still have questions for you.}Stále mám na tebe pár otázek.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:20.00,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{You're not escaping to the afterlife!}Neunikneš do posmrtného života.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:22.25,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Then you will die together.}Potom zemřete společně.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:23.92,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Kakihara-san!}Pane Kakiharo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.64,0:16:28.65,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Tsubasa!}Tsubaso!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:34.36,Shinsou main,AERO,0000,0000,0000,,{Kakihara-san.}Kakiharo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.27,0:16:42.53,Shinsou main,MARIE,0000,0000,0000,,{Live.}Žij.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:46.40,Shinsou main,AERO,0000,0000,0000,,{Live.}Žij.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.96,0:16:51.05,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Tsubasa!}Tsubaso!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.08,0:16:57.32,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{No need to grieve. Death is\N but a moment's parting.}Není třeba se trápit. Smrt je okamžik rozloučení.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:01.00,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Kakihara-san?}Pane Kakiharo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:06.67,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{I hear the wailing of your soul.}Slyším nářek tvé duše.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.97,0:17:08.40,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Shut up!}Drž hubu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:12.31,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{You're one more note.}Jsi nota navíc.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.31,0:17:15.93,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{Play for me the rhapsody of death.}Zahraj mi melodii smrti.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.91,0:17:20.39,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Kakihara-san!}Kakiharo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.82,0:17:29.09,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Cerdid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.58,0:17:32.29,Shinsou main,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{You'll pay for hurting Chihiro!}Zaplatíš za to, že lovíš Chihira!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.95,0:17:36.48,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Why did you save me?}Proč jte mě zachránil?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.83,0:17:43.16,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Making you admit your guilt \Nwas my life's purpose.}Donutit tě přiznat vinu, byl můj životní úděl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:47.47,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{I didn't want to acknowledge\N that my parents rejected me.}Nechci vědět, proč mě rodiče opustili.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:50.98,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{If you love someone,\N you should take them with you.}Když někoho miluješ, měl bys ho vzít sebou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:55.68,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{So I couldn't forgive you for\N refusing to die with him.}Takže ti nemohu odpustit, že jsi odmítl umřít s ním.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:18:00.28,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{But it seems I was wrong.}Vypadá to, že jsem se mýlil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:01.82,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{I lost sight of the tru—}Ztrati jsem ponětí o prav—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.82,0:18:02.64,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Kakihara-san!}Pane Kakiharo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.99,0:18:04.64,Shinsou main,CERDID,0000,0000,0000,,{Chihiro, run!}Chihiro, uteč!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.63,0:18:08.90,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{You didn't kill your father.}Ty jsi svého otce nezabil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.34,0:18:12.90,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{I reviewed the case documents again.}Prohlédl jsem si složky znovu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:18.53,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{He must have returned to his\Nsenses when he was stabbed.}Musel se mu vrátit cit když byl bodnut.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.15,0:18:25.08,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{He feared his own actions\N and knew he had to save you.}Bál se svých vlastních akcí a věděl, že tě musí zachránit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.67,0:18:29.45,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{So you wouldn't be a murderer.}Takže bys neměl být vrah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.90,0:18:33.50,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{So you'd live.}Tak bys měl žít.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:35.30,sign_26669_270_Live,,0000,0000,0000,,{Live}Žij.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.15,0:18:39.30,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{I didn't kill my father...}Nezabil jsem svého otce...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:41.84,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{You didn't kill him!}Nezabil jsi svého otce.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.73,0:18:44.93,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Kark!}Karku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:53.46,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Kakihara-san!}Pane Kakiharo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.13,0:18:56.82,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Are you okay, Chihiro-san?!}Jsi v pořádku, Chihiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:19:00.20,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Kotetsu, that's the man who killed Kurokami-san!}Kotetsu, to je ten muž který zabil Kurokami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:02.47,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{That bastard killed Marie?}Ten šmejd zabil Marii?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:04.46,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Let's go, Kotecchan!}Jdem na to, Kotíku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.46,0:19:05.20,Shinsou main,KOTETSU,0000,0000,0000,,{Yeah.}Jo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.48,0:19:07.33,Shinsou main,KARK,0000,0000,0000,,{That's all for today.}To je pro dnešek vše.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.20,0:19:10.17,Shinsou main,TSUBAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{Hey, wait!}Hej, počkej!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.06,0:19:14.17,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Cerdid...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:18.93,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{No...}Ne...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.93,0:19:20.87,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Don't you feel relieved?}Neulevilo se ti?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:27.25,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{It's not like me to die protecting you.}Není to tak, že bych umřel pro tvou ochranu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.01,0:19:33.26,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Maybe I was jealous.}Možná jsem žárlil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.41,0:19:33.94,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{What?}Co?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.23,0:19:37.01,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Nothing. It's in the past now.}Nic. Je to minulost.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:41.95,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{In the end, you and I were the same.}Nakonec, jsme ty a já byli stejní.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.25,0:19:45.63,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Sorry.}Promiň.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.82,0:19:48.73,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{It's fine.}To je v pořádku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.91,0:19:50.84,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Live.}Žij.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:54.56,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Live, Kamina Chihiro.}Žij, Kamino Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.11,0:20:00.21,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Kurokami, Akaya Inuki, Tsubasa,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.81,0:20:04.80,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{your father, and I have a message for you.}tvůj otec a já máme pro tebe zprávu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.92,0:20:08.70,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{You have to live. Live.}Musíš žít. Žij.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.35,0:20:10.66,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Kakihara-san...}Pane Kakiharo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.66,0:20:13.33,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{There's a reason you survived.}Je důvod proč jsi přežil.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:20.50,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Maybe I was left alive\N so I could tell you this.}Možná, že jsem zůstal naživu jen proto, abych ti to mohl říct.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.47,0:20:26.14,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Someday, you'll tell someone...}Jednoho dne, řekneš někomu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.23,0:20:29.31,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Kakihara-san. Kakihara-san...}Pane Kakiharo. Pane Kakiharo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.31,0:20:30.65,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Tsubasa...}Tsubaso...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.11,0:20:37.71,Shinsou main,KAKIHARA,0000,0000,0000,,{Dad, Mom...}Tati, Mami...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.27,0:20:39.54,Shinsou main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{Kakihara-san!}Pane Kakiharo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.02,0:20:50.19,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Another.}Další.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.87,0:20:53.41,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Fate is truly unfaithful.}Osud je skutečně nepřesný.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.41,0:20:57.85,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{When Kotetsu was spared,\NI thought it was a rare blessing.}Když jsem ušetřila Kotetsa, myslela jsem si, že je to vzácné požehnání.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.43,0:21:00.00,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{So why, why?}Tak proč, proč?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:02.94,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{However, at this rate...}Nicméně, při této rychlosti ...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:05.91,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Yes. They'll be annihilated again.}Ano. Budou znovu zničeni.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.65,0:21:07.65,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Again?}Znovu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.18,0:21:13.41,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Even if Tokyo is destroyed,\N Chaos' plan may not be stopped.}Dokonce i tehdy, když je Tokio zničeno, se Chaosův plán nezastaví.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.55,0:21:17.78,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{If the last one is connected, there\N will be a Second Great Collapse.}Dokud je jediný připojen, nastane druhé velké zhroucení.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.15,0:21:20.70,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{Chaos wins.}Chaos vyhraje.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.28,0:21:23.26,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{I will not let that happen.}Nedopustím aby se tak stalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.19,0:21:26.43,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{The time has come to settle this.}Nastal čas to urovnat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.13,0:21:32.43,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{We cannot retreat until we're down\Nto the last of the Heroic Lineage.}Nemůžeme ustoupit dokud někdo z hrdinské linie zbývá.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.82,0:21:35.15,Shinsou main,SHOKO,0000,0000,0000,,{Yes, absolutely.}Ano, jistě.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.85,0:21:39.16,Shinsou main,DUX,0000,0000,0000,,{For the splendid new world.}Pro nádherný nový svět.
